rings.1: Kip and swing elements & swings through or to handstand
rings.2: Strength elements and hold elements (2 sec.)
rings.3: Swing to Strength hold elements (2 sec.)

pommel horse.2: Circle and flairs, with and/or without spindles and handstands, Kehr -swings, Russian w., flops and combined elements
pommel horse.3: Travel type elements, including Krolls, Tong Fei, Wu Guonian, Roth and Traveling Spindles

vault.1: Single salto vaults with complex twists
vault.2: Handspring salto vaults with or without simple twists, and all double salto fwd.
vault.3: Handspring with ¼ or ½ turn in the 1st flight phase

parallel bars.1: Elements in support or through support on 2 bars
parallel bars.2: Elements starting in upper arm position
parallel bars.3: Long swings in hang en 1 or 2 bars and Underswings
